I would really give this 1.5 forks -- somewhere between okay and good. I was just disappointed in this recipe because there's not much going on with it. I will make this again, but next time would add hot italian sausage, black olives, red pepper flakes, some green peppers with the onions, etc. This was just way too bland for our taste.

